<span id="freeTextContainer9067420724961177495">Do you know what&apos;s wrong with this New Direction edition of West&apos;s most famous two little novels? Nothing. It&apos;s a perfect book. And it&apos;s a work that never gets old. The ultimate Hollywood nove (Day of the...)l that is almost spiritual. West got it right away and very few could match his greatness or snickering. A snicker that becomes passionate.<br/><br/>Miss Lonelyhearts is awesome beyond one&apos;s favorite mustard. It&apos;s a nasty little book that still stings. Hail West!</span>
  <span id="freeText9067420724961177495" style="display:none">Do you know what's wrong with this New Direction edition of West's most famous two little novels? Nothing. It's a perfect book. And it's a work that never gets old. The ultimate Hollywood nove (Day of the...)l that is almost spiritual. West got it right away and very few could match his greatness or snickering. A snicker that becomes passionate.<br /><br />Miss Lonelyhearts is awesome beyond one's favorite mustard. It's a nasty little book that still stings. Hail West!</span>
